# Data Dictionary

Column definitions for the Customer Churn Analytics Dashboard dataset.

---

## Customer Table

| Column | Type | Description | Example Values |
|--------|------|-------------|----------------|
| CustomerID | Text | Unique customer identifier | C-00001 |
| Churned | Text | Whether the customer has churned | Yes / No |
| Tenure | Integer | Months as a customer | 0–72 |
| TenureBand | Text | Grouped tenure range (calculated) | 0-6 Months, 6-12 Months, 1-2 Years, 2+ Years |
| MonthlyCharges | Decimal | Monthly subscription charge | 20.00–120.00 |
| TotalCharges | Decimal | Cumulative charges to date | — |
| ContractType | Text | Contract length | Month-to-Month, One Year, Two Year |
| PaymentMethod | Text | How the customer pays | Bank Transfer, Credit Card, Electronic Check |
| Gender | Text | Customer gender | Male / Female |
| SeniorCitizen | Integer | Whether the customer is a senior | 0 / 1 |
| Partner | Text | Whether the customer has a partner | Yes / No |
| Dependants | Text | Whether the customer has dependants | Yes / No |
| PhoneService | Text | Has phone service | Yes / No |
| InternetService | Text | Internet service type | DSL, Fibre Optic, No |
| OnlineSecurity | Text | Has online security add-on | Yes / No / No Internet Service |
| TechSupport | Text | Has tech support add-on | Yes / No / No Internet Service |
| StreamingTV | Text | Has streaming TV | Yes / No / No Internet Service |

---

## Notes

- All personally identifiable information has been removed or anonymised
- MonthlyCharges and TotalCharges have been cleaned to remove blank strings converted to nulls
- Churned field was originally encoded as 0/1 integer and converted to Yes/No text in Power Query
- TenureBand is a calculated column created in DAX (see dax_measures.md)
